column5: Any nice campgrounds within an hour of Simcoe??????  I have a wedding nearby and thought I would check out this area,I,ve never been before.
Lake Simcoe or Simcoe the town/city. They are not even close to one another. If it is Lake Simcoe then as aboce Sibald has a nice launch and beach for kids.
lots of PP in the area look them up.  Some are right on the lake.
